constant velocity:
(x, y) = (x, y) + (v_x, v_y) * time_diff
loc[0] = loc[0] + v * cos(θ) * time_diff
loc[1] = loc[1] + v * sin(θ) * time_diff

x: without B
| 1,     cos(θ) * time_diff | * | x | = | x + v * (cos(θ) * time_diff) |
| 0,     1					|	| v |	| 0 + v                        |

| 1 0 | * | x | = | true_x |
| 0 1 |   | v |	  | true_v |



